title: Lost Civilizations! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 79
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes are indulging in some government conspiracies. The yellow brick road found on the bottom of the Pacific ocean. Shout out Graham Hancock!!! What is Göbekli Tepe and how does it impact history? In the 5th grade Sal attacked religion in front of the whole class. Youtube is an addiction. Ancient forest found in sink hole in China. A dead eye ball is brought back to life. Would you opt out of death if possible? Would you wanna outlive everybody? What is the Mandela effect? How will we be remembered in the future? Chris teaches Sal about MK-Ultra. Lost civilizations have peaked Chris' interest! How do full societies go missing? Imagine 5,000 years in the future......Chris goes in on some youtube rabbit holes. Don't let people ruin your day. Was Noah's Ark a hoax?!? Chris has an amazing Fat Joe story. Crazy fight happens in front of the Comedy Cellar.
